CommonFields.Title: Preparation and characterization of graphite nano-platelet (GNP)/epoxy nano-composite: Mechanical, electrical and thermal properties
Author: Chandrasekaran, Swetha
Seidel, Christian
Schulte, Karl
CommonFields.Location: Institut für Kunststoffe und Verbundwerkstoffe, Technische Universität Hamburg-Harburg, Denickestrasse, 15, D-21073 Hamburg, Germany

Mixing.Description: The GNPs were dispersed in epoxy matrix using a three-roll mill. The gap between the feed roll and the apron roll was varied from 120 micrometers down to 5 micrometers and the whole suspension was milled seven times in total in order to achieve a uniform dispersion.

XRay_Diffraction_and_Scattering.Equipment: Brucker AXS – D8 Advance X-ray diffractometer
